bloodsucker-mesmerize-starting = You begin to hypnotically gaze at {$target}...
bloodsucker-mesmerize-success = You successfully mesmerize {$target}.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-unconscious = {$target} is not conscious.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-bloodsucker = Bloodsuckers are immune to mesmerize.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-eyes-covered = Your eyes are concealed from sight.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-blind-self = You have no eyes with which to mesmerize.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-blind-target = {$target} is blind.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-not-facing = You must be facing {$target}.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-target-not-facing = {$target} must be facing you.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-already = {$target} is already in a hypnotic gaze.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-fail-chaplain = Your gaze slides off their faith.
bloodsucker-mesmerize-chaplain-resist = You feel your eyes burn for a while, but it passes.

